{"word":"Decalogue","slug":"decalogue","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Decalogue</b> Written by God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=12'>Exo 24:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=31&verse=18'>Exo 31:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=16'>Exo 32:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=5&verse=22'>Deu 5:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=10'>Deu 9:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=8&verse=12'>Hos 8:12</a><br/> Divine authority of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=1'>Exo 20:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=28'>Exo 34:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=5&verse=22'>Deu 5:22</a><br/> Called Words of the Covenant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=28'>Exo 34:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=13'>Deu 4:13</a><br/> Called Tables of Testimony<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=31&verse=18'>Exo 31:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=29'>Exo 34:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=20'>Exo 40:20</a><br/><a href='S:Commandments'>Commandments</a><br/> Examples of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=17'>Exo 20:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=5&verse=21'>Deu 5:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=19'>Mat 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=40'>Mat 22:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=28'>Luk 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=13&verse=10'>Rom 13:10</a>"}]}